quran[85]{c,v,t}:
  40,1,"Haa, miim."
  40,2,"Jippagol deftere nde, ko immorde e Allah, pool…óo, ganndo oon."
  40,3,"Kaforoowo bakkatuuji …óin, Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee, ca…ótu…óo lepte, Joom yaajeende. Dewetee…óo alaa, si wonaa kaŇčko. Ko ka makko woni ruttorde nden."
  40,4,"Alaa ko wee√Īdata e aayeeje Allah …óen, si wonaa yeddu…ďe …ďen. Wota a hoditor ko …ďe dillirta kon ka leydi."
  40,5,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďeen e pe…óle …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, yedduno (Nulaa…ďe mum …ďeen), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun oon. ∆Āe njeddiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Min nanngi …ďe. Taskii no nanngal am ngal wa…ótinirnoo !"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yeddu…ďe …ďeen : ""Won'de pellet, ko …ďe yim…ďe Yiite""."
  40,7,"∆Āeen (Malaa'ikaa…ďe) roondii…ďe Arsiki kin, e won…ďe bannge makki …ďen, hi…ďe cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngooŇč…óina mo, …ďe insinorana gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen (wiide): ""Joomi amen, A ya√Ī√Īirii kala hu'unde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan …ďen tuubu…ďe, …ďe njokki laawol Maa ngol, da…óndaa …ďe kadi lepte Dul…ďoowe ngeen."
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naadu…ďe ka Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …óin …ói podu…óaa …ďe, e kala mo∆ī∆īu…óo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, e genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, e ge√Īngol ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, ko Aan woni poolu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo Oon."
  40,9,"Da…óndaa…ďe [kuu…óe] e bon…óe …óen. Kala mo da…óndu…óaa [kuu…óe] mum bon…óe …óen nden √Ďande, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo"". Ko …óum woni maloore mawnunde ndeen."
  40,10,"Yeddu…ďe …ďeen noddiroyte: ""Ko tikkere Allah nden …ďuri mawnude, e dii ko tikkan…óon ko'e mon …óum, tuma noddeteno…óon e gooŇč…óinal, njeddon."
  40,11,"∆Āe mbi'a: ""Joomi amen, A warii min laawi …ói…ói, nguurnu…óaa min laawi …ói…ói: min qirrike bakkaat amen …óin. Taw si laawol jaltirngol hino woodi?""."
  40,12,"""∆äuum moo…óon, ko tawde si Allah tan noddanooma, on njeddon; si O kafidaama, ngooŇč…óinon. √Ďaawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, Toow…óo, Maw…óo On""."
  40,13,"Ko KaŇčko woni kolloowo on Ma'andeeji makko …óin, o jippinirana on to…ďo ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wonaa nduttotoo…óo [e Allah]."
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, la…ď…ďinirangol mo diina kan, hay si he'efer…ďe …ďeen nj…óaa."
  40,15,"Ko o toowu…óo darjaaji, Jey…óo Arsi kin. Homo jippiniria wahayu oon, yamiroore makko, e on mo o muuyani e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen, no o jeertinirde √Īalnde Kawral ngal,"
  40,16,"√Īande …ďe fee√Īoyta. Hu'unde suu…óotaako Allah, e fee ma…ď…ďe. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, poolu…óo On."
  40,17,"Hannde, woŇčkii kala yo…ďete ko faggitii. Too√Īe woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko √Īaaw…óo √Īaawoore."
  40,18,"Jeertnirt…ďe, √Īalaande dillere nden, tuma …ďer…óe …óen ∆īawtirta ka konondi, hara he…ďe (heewu…ďe) ngo∆īo. Gi…óo woo alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen, wonaa tefoowo ja…ďantee…óo."
  40,19,"Homo anndi njamfa gite, e ko …ďer…óe …óeen cuu…ói."
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga √Īaawirta. ∆äi …ďe ndeewata …óiin non, gaanin makko, hay hu'unde …ói √Īaawirtaa. Pellet, ko kaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  40,21,"Hara …ďee njiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe ndaara no battane ado mabbe …ďen wa'unoo? ∆Āeen le no …ďurunoo tii…óude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri …ďe bakkaauuji ma…ď…ďe …óiin, …ďe he…ďaano da…óndoowo …ďe e (lepte) Allah …óeen."
  40,22,"Ko wa…ói …óuum, ko tawde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ngaddatno …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, …ďe njedda. Allah halki …ďe. Pellet, ko O Doolnu…óo, ca…ótu…óo lepte."
  40,23,"GooŇč…óii Min nulirii Muusaa aayeeje Amen …óen, e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono …ďe mbi'i: ""Ko bileejo, …óuu…óu…óo penaande!""."
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo …ďe goonga ka, immorde e amen, …ďe mb'iti: ""mbaree …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen e makko, accon rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen"". Pewje he'efer…ďe …ďen wonaani, si wonaa e majjere."
  40,26,"Fir'awna wi'i: ""ngccee mi wara Muusaa. Yo o noddu Joomi makko ! Mi…óo huli nde o waylata diina mon kan, maa o fe√Ī√Īina bonnere e leydi""."
  40,27,"Muusa maaki: ""Mi moolorii Jey…óo kam on, jeyi on, e bone kala mawnintinii…óo, mo gooŇč…óinaa √Īalaande hasboore""."
  40,28,"Gorko gooŇč…óin…óo goo, jiyaa…óo e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen - cuu…óunoo…óo gooŇč…óinal mum - :""E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: ""Joomi am ko Allah?"" Hara le o addanii on …ďanngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kaŇčko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, he…ďay on"". Pellet, Allah feewnata on fantinoowo yeddoowo!"
  40,29,"Eey yo yim…ďe am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, ko on fool…ďe ka leydi. Kono ko hommbo wallata en, e lepte Allah …óen, si …óe ngarii e men?"" Fir'awna wi'i: ""Mi hollataa on, si wanaa ko mi yi'i kon. Mi tindintaa on kadi, si wonaa e laawol peewal ngol""."
  40,30,"GooŇč…óin…óo on wi'iti: ""eey mon yo yim…ďe am, min on mi…óo hulani on, sugu √Īalaande he…ďunoonde pe…óle …óin."
  40,31,"Sugu mbowka yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďeen, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arnoo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďen"". Allah faandanaaki too√Īde jiyaa…ďe …ďen."
  40,32,"Eey mon yim…ďe am, miin mi…óo hulani on, √Ďalaande noddindirton"
  40,33,"√Ďalnde nduŇčtindroyton, ho…óon ndoga, hara da…óndoowo on alanaa on e Allah"". Kala mo Allah majjini, haray peewnoowo alanaa mo."
  40,34,"GooŇč…óii Yuusufu ardanii on e …ďannganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraani e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, mbiu…óon: ""Allah nultataa Nulaa…óo goo, …ďaawo makko"". Ko non majjinirta kala gon…óo fantinoowo cikkitii…óo."
  40,35,"∆Āeen wee√Īiroo…ďe e aayeeje Allah …óen ko aldaa e hujja ar…óo …ďe, [kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen. Ko wano non Allah notirta e …ďernde kala mawnintinii…óo dundarankeejo."
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: "" eey ma yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo …óate …óen."
  40,37,"…óate kammuuji …óin, mi ∆īeewoya Dewetee…óo Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo penoowo"". Ko wano non Fir'awna du…óiranaa, golle makko bon…óe …óen; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wonaa e hayrere."
  40,38,"[Gorko] gooŇč…óin…óo on wi'i: ""eey mon yo yim…ďe am, njokkee kam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol."
  40,39,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe am, nganndee …óam nguurndam aduna, ko ndakamme-hun tun, ko La'akara on woni, galle √Īii…ďal …óen."
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yo…ďitetaake, si wonaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi mo∆ī∆īere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gooŇč…óin…óo, …ďeen …óoon naatay Aljanna, …ďe arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore."
  40,41,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óal, ho…óon nodda kam e Yiite?"
  40,42,"Hi…óon nodda kam e jeddugol Allah, sirkana mo e ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo nodda on e pool…óo, cuhuroowo bakkaat Oon."
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, won'de ko noddoton kam e mum kon, dewal alanaa …óum aduna, wonaa La'akara. E won'de ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e won'de ko fantim…ďe …ďeen, ngoni Yiite ngen."
  40,44,"Aray nde nganndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko deen…óo jiyaa…ďe …ďen""."
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ďe pewjunoo, o fiiltii yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen, ko …ďuri bon'de e lepte."
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, …ďe mbee…ďitoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √Ďande darnga daroytoo (wi'oyte): ""Naatee yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen, ka …ďuri sa…ótude e lepte""."
  40,47,"JaŇčto tuma …ďe yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unoo…ďe …ďen wi'ana townitinoo…ďe …ďeen: ""Minen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on du√Īanay men ge…óal e Yiite ngeen?"""
  40,48,"Townitinoo…ďe …ďeen mbi'a: ""En fof, hi…óen e magge. GooŇč…óii Allah √Īaawii hakkunde jiyaa…ďe …ďen""."
  40,49,"Won…ďe ka Yiite …ďen kadi mbi'ana ayninaa…ďe Jahannama …ďen: ""Toranee min Joomi mon, O hoynana men, √Īalaande (wootere) e lepte …óen""."
  40,50,"∆Āe mbi'a: ""Nulaa…ďe mon …ďen ardanaano on e …ďanngannduyeeji?"" ∆Āe mbi'a: ""oo'owoye !"" [Ayninaa…ďe] …ďen wi'a: ""Awa toree, onon tigiri !"" Kono toraare he'efer…ďe …ďen ngonaani, si wanaa e majjere."
  40,51,"Pellet, Min mballay Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, e gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďen, ka nguurndam aduna, e √Ďalnde seedee…ďe …ďeen daroytoo,"
  40,52,"√Īalnde de ngantinagol nafoytaa too√Īnoo…ďe …ďeen, hara kuddi hino woodani …ďe, e galle bon…óe."
  40,53,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkii Muusaa ganndal [Tawreeta] ngal, Min ndonini …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen, deftere nden."
  40,54,"ko nde peewal e waaju, wona nde joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."
  40,55,"Mu√Ī√Īo tan, pellet, fodoore Allah nden ko goonga, imsinano bakkaatuuji maa …óiin, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa, kiikii…óe e bimmbi."
  40,56,"Pellet, wee√Īiniroo…ďe e aayeeje Allah …óeen, ko aldaa e dalil ar…óo e ma…ď…ďe, alaa e …ďer…óe …óen, si wonaa mawnintinagol. ∆Āe yottotaako noon, e …óuum. Moolor Allah, Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  40,57,"Pellet, ko takde kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, …ďuri mawnude e dii tageendi yim…ďe …ďeen. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe nganndaa."
  40,58,"Bum…óo e ji'oowo potataa, gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďeen kadi ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, potataa e bon…óo. Fam…óii ko mbajitorton !"
  40,59,"Pellet, Darnga, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'um. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďeen, …ďe ngoŇč…óinaa."
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: ""Toree Kam, Mi jaabinana on. Mawtinantoo…ďe dewugol Lam …ďeen, ko pellet, …ďe naatoyay Jahannama, ko …ďe hoy…ďe""."
  40,61,"Ko Allah wa…óirani on jemma on, ka fowto…óon e mum, e √Īalawma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ďural e yim…ďe …ďen, kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe njettataa (neema)."
  40,62,"Ko oon moo…óon Allah Joomi mon, woni Tak…óo kala huunde. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko honno pirlitorta…óon (e …óuum?)"
  40,63,"Ko noon …ďeya yeddatnoo…ďe aayeeje Allah …óeen, perlisortenoo."
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni ba…óiran…óo on leydi ndin, √Īii…ďirde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O mo∆ī∆īini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laa…ďu…ói. Ko oon moo…óon woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden !"
  40,65,"Ko KaŇčko woni guur…óo Oon. Dewetee…óo alaa, si wonaa KaŇčko. Ndewee Mo kisan; la…ď…ďinano mo diina kan. Jettooje ngoodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere ndeen !"
  40,66,"Maaku: ""Miin mi ha…óaama dewugol …óiin …ói noddoton ga Allah, tuma nde …ďannganduyeeji …óin ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, Jey…óo winndere ndeen""."
  40,67,"Ko KaŇčko woni tak…óo on e mbumbuldi, refti e to…ď…ďere (maniiyu), refti e he…ó…óere, refti o yaltiniri on penuu…ďe fii no njottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayee…ďe, - no e mo'on, ∆īettitetee…ďe ado …óuum, - haa no njottoron lajal kappaangal, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  40,68,"Ko KaŇčko woni guurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anat mo tan: ""Laato"", o laatoo."
  40,69,"E a tinaani, …ďeen yeddondirtee…ďe e aayeeje Allah …óeen, ko honno …ďe pirlitoraa?"
  40,70,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe deftere ndeen, e kon ko Min nuliri nulaa…ďe Amen …ďeen; …ďe ngaray anndude,"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje …óen mba…óoyaa e daa…óe ma…ď…ďe, e jolokooje(callalle) …óeen, hara he…ďe ndaasiree"
  40,72,"ka ndeer ngul…óam; refti …ďe hu…ď…ďoyee ka ndeer Yiite."
  40,73,"refti …ďe mbi'anee: ""Ko holto woni …óin …ói kafidatno…óon?"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?"" ∆Āe mbi'a: ""∆äi majjitike min. Wurin, min ngonaano ko adii, e dewugol hay hu'unde"". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta he'efer…ďe …ďen."
  40,75,"Ko wa…ói on …óuum, ko ko mbeltoratno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko mbliratno…óon kon."
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óeen, luttugol ton. nge bonii jaa∆īorde wona'de mawnintinii…ďe …ďeen!."
  40,77,"Mu√Ī√Īo. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Min hollete yoga e ko Min podi …ďe kon, maa hara Min ∆īettite (ado mum) ko ka Amen …ďe ruttirtee."
  40,78,"GooŇč…óii Min imminii Nulaa…ďe ado maa. Hino e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Min cifani maa fii mum; hino ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Min cifanaaki ma fii mum. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol aaya, si wonaa e duŇčayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √Īaawirte meerente'en sooya nden √Īalnde."
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo On neemoraa…ói …óin ko mba…ó…óoron, √Īaamon kadi e majji."
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino ngoodani on e majji, e no njottoron e majji, haaju hittu…óo e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laa…óe …óeen, woni ko ndonndete…óon."
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji makko …óin. Ko hol…óum e Ma'andeeji Allah …óin, woni ko njeddoton?"
  40,82,"E …ďee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe ndaara ko holno battane …ďeya ado ma…ď…ďe mbattinirnoo? ∆Āen no …ďurunoo …ďe …óuude e sa…ótude doole e batteeji [wa…óaa…ói] ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ďe paggotonoo, duncanaano …ďe."
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addannoo…ďe …ďanngannduyeeji …óin, …ďe wewliri ganndal ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon. ∆Āe kuu…ďitiraa kon ko …ďe njalkitaynoo."
  40,84,"Nde …ďe nii'unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ďe mbi'i: ""Min ngooŇč…óinii Allah tan, min yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e cirkannde""."
  40,85,"Kono ngooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe wonaano ko nafata …ďe, feewndo …ďe nji'unoo lepte Amen …óeen; …óum ko laawol Allah non, gooŇč…óii …óun yawtiino e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Yeddu…ďe …ďen sooyi …óon nden √Īalnde."
